Millions of South Africans are expected to cast their votes on Wednesday for the 2019 national and provincial elections. From repeating the same jokes in all 11 official languages to taking his morning walks, we followed the man at the helm of the ANC, Cyril Ramaphosa, on his campaign trail over the last couple of months to show you his different faces. Ramaphosa has had to embody many different characters in order to convince South Africans to vote for the ANC - but will it be enough?